des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : feedback@tuyasmart.me
Amazon Alexa and the Nooie Home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the plug. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home plug - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Nooie Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Nooie Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Nooie Home account in our "Nooie Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Nooie Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Nooie Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Nooie Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Nooie Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Nooie Home", and you'll be navigated to Tuya login page;
(9). Input your Tuya account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen plug"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen plug"

Currently this skill supports products:
Nooie Home Plug
